name: go fu*k yourself.

This cryptocurrency represents freedom for those unafraid to challenge norms and break barriers. It also speaks to those who feel they have nothing left but the courage to say the right three words. Elon Musk has not only inspired the creation of our project but continues to serve as a thought leader for our community. Join our community and help transform cryptocurrency into what it was always meant to be.
